Asda recalled Little Angels 2 Newborn Soothers 0+ after a customer complaint on Facebook . 
  The teat detached from the hard casing of one of the dummies . 
  It is the second time in two years that the supermarket has issued a recall over a choking risk . 
  In January 2013 the Little Angels Cherry Soother was recalled after one came apart in a baby's mouth . 
  Customers have been asked to dispose of the products or return them to Asda . 
 